4 European Athletics Championships, as well as claiming victory at the World Indoor Championships in March.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 European Athletics Championships\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Indoor Championships\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She secured a deal to become an Adidas athlete after a fifth place finish at the World Championships in Budapest last August.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999959977686, \"rank\": 3.800172667143571e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a deal\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"an Adidas athlete\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth place finish\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Success at the Games next week will only see her fame and wealth grow even more exponentially.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Success\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"her fame\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"wealth\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this could be just the beginning for Caudery as she looks to transcend her sport, according to sports finance expert Rob Wilson.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 825, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Scott_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9999744531