to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"camera well\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1467}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she maintains her sporting commitments, as with Keely, we would be talking about earnings in excess of \\u00a310m.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sporting commitments\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"earnings\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"excess\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a310m.\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If linked to modelling and its associated industries, this figure could be ten times that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"modelling\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"this figure\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"ten times that\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999909723556, \"rank\": 9.02750233450213e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The streamer\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"3,800 hours\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \